{"tid":1406400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我好鍾意返工呀！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T13:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:20:28.000Z","uid":142354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d9068cd95dc439b704c372e97401a6b18d5f6bb7","tid":1406400,"uid":142354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我係一個好鍾意返工嘅香港人 <br />\n而我又好好彩咁有個好鍾意我返工嘅老細同埋同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然香港呢個地方成日塞車 地鐵又成日停駛<br />\n但係聰明嘅我都從未遲過到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事關老細教落巴士塞車就搭地鐵 地鐵停駛就搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近個個都話8月5號要罷工 仲要搞啲咩塞車連動<br />\n我好擔心聽日地面地底一齊塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果聽日巴士地鐵一直塞落去通唔到車<br />\n一個唔好彩塞下塞下返到公司已經到左食飯時間咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想公司運作唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家聽日高抬貴手唔好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">塞哂路面同地鐵<br />\n尤其是係地鐵啲轉綫站！！！</span></span><br />\n平時已經成日上唔到車 <br />\n呢啲大站塞一陣真係排到出出口都唔夠位企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老細要我影相update situation</span></span>嘅時候發現我係街以為我罷工點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我好希望大家聽日一齊返工 朝早一齊等巴士等地鐵！！！！<br />\n一齊享受返工呢條無止境嘅路途嘅樂趣啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n依家啲後生愈嚟愈唔鍾意返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要光復下等大家知道返工嘅美至得！<br />\n聽日一齊等車返工呀知道未！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"655303a61c7203f566e2e90f31e9eb1ede4d8121","tid":1406400,"uid":142354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"第一次開po就highlight漏野 係唔好塞哂巴士地鐵至啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4e35e27788d5ccbbc47d5e071ff648eb5b1ece","tid":1406400,"uid":267235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該入一入黎幫手推post</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【8.5三罷】如果朝早所有人遊車河!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404800</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cc3YftZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCc3YftZ.png&h=73d6d6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUfS7Za.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUfS7Za.png&h=2961d